Item 12. Disclosure of Results of Operations and Financial Condition
     On July 30, 2003, Akamai Technologies, Inc. announced its financial results for the quarter ended June 30, 2003. The full text of the press release issued in connection with the announcement is attached as Exhibit 99.1 to this Current Report on Form 8-K.
