EXPLANATORY NOTE
On June 16, 2005, Akamai Technologies, Inc. ("Akamai or the "Registrant") filed a Current Report on Form 8-K relating to its acquisition of Speedera Networks Inc. ("Speedera") that excluded certain financial statements that were not available at the time of filing. On August 26, 2005, Akamai amended the original Current Report on Form 8-K (the "Form 8-K/A") to include required financial statements and pro forma financial information in connection with the Speedera acquisition. By this amendment, Akamai is filing supplemental pro forma financial information in connection with the Speedera acquisition that includes an unaudited combined condensed pro forma statement of operations for the full year ended December 1, 2005, prepared as if the acquisition of Speedera had occurred on January 1, 2005.
