Akamai will host a conference call today at 4:30 p.m. ET that can be accessed through 1-800-510-9834 (or 1-617-614-3669 for international calls) and using passcode No. 93777894. A live Webcast of the call may be accessed at in the Investor section. In addition, a replay of the call will be available for one week following the conference through the Akamai Website or by calling 1-888-286-8010 (or 1-617-801-6888 for international calls) and using passcode No. 78517440.
www.akamai.com
